OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980701
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FA former Hampshire police officer who
OL,8,Fcarried out unwarranted strip searches
OL,9,Fon young men in custody has been found
OL,10,Fguilty of a series of sexual offences.
OL,12,FGerard Hutchings, 66, a former
OL,13,Finspector with Hampshire Police, made
OL,14,Fyoung men remove their clothes before
OL,15,Fsubjecting them to sexual assaults.
OL,17,FBristol Crown Court heard eight
OL,18,Fcomplainants said they were abused by
OL,19,FHutchings at police stations in the
OL,20,FHampshire area over an eight-year
OL,21,Fperiod.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
