FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980701
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FHutchings had denied 11 charges ` five
OL,8,Fof indecent assault, five of causing a
OL,9,Fperson to engage in a sexual activity
OL,10,Fwithout consent and one of misconduct
OL,11,Fin public office ` but was convicted
OL,12,Fon all counts by the jury.
OL,14,FHe had admitted 17 counts of
OL,15,Fmisconduct in a public office at a
OL,16,Fprevious hearing.
OL,18,FThe charges related to a total of 18
OL,19,Fvictims who were alone with Hutchings
OL,20,Fin his private office at the police
OL,21,Fstation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
