FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980701
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FThe court heard the complainants `
OL,8,Faged in their late teens to early 30s
OL,9,Fand who cannot be identified for legal
OL,10,Freasons ` had been arrested for minor
OL,11,Foffences, such as shoplifting and
OL,12,Fpossessing cannabis.
OL,14,FThey reported being subject to an
OL,15,Funjustified and illegal strip search
OL,16,Fby Hutchings, while being administered
OL,17,Fa caution or reprimand for a minor
OL,18,Foffence. He also sexually assaulted
OL,19,Fsome of them during these procedures.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980701
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FDuring the trial, eight victims gave
OL,8,Fevidence of how they felt during these
OL,9,Funwarranted strip search procedures.
OL,11,FOne victim, who had been arrested for
OL,12,Fshoplifting, described how he was
OL,13,F"humiliated" by Hutchings.
OL,15,F"There was nothing ordinary that day.
OL,16,FHe was trying to humiliate me. I am
OL,17,Fwell aware of the things done to me
OL,18,Fand he was trying to humiliate me," he
OL,19,Ftold the jury.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
