PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980702
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,F"I do believe he took great pleasure
OL,8,Fin pointing out what a piece of scum I
OL,9,Fwas and people like me should not walk
OL,10,Fthe earth, or words to that effect.
OL,12,F"I have been strip searched before and
OL,13,Fthere was no following of the rules
OL,14,Fwhatsoever. He never took any interest
OL,15,Fin my clothing."
OL,17,FHutchings had previously been jailed
OL,18,Fin 2008 after admitting 11 misconduct
OL,19,Fin a public office offences for
OL,20,Fsimilar offending.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
