PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980702
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FHampshire Police sacked him in 2007
OL,8,Fafter the complaints were made
OL,9,Ffollowing a fast-track disciplinary
OL,10,Fprocedure.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
