FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980702
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FIn 2020, the force started a new
OL,8,Finvestigation after receiving a report
OL,9,Ffrom a man who had been subject to a
OL,10,Fsimilar strip search in 2005. As part
OL,11,Fof the investigation, officers cross-
OL,12,Freferenced Hutchings' police notebook
OL,13,Fwith police records to identify 373
OL,14,Fpeople who came into contact with him
OL,15,Fat a station.
OL,17,FAll those people were visited in
OL,18,Fperson by officers, who used a non-
OL,19,Fleading questionnaire to establish
OL,20,Fwhether they had been subject to any
OL,21,Foffences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980702
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FFrom there, a further 17 people
OL,8,Fprovided statements on video detailing
OL,9,Ftheir experience of Hutchings.
OL,11,FTemporary Deputy Chief Constable Rob
OL,12,FFrance said: "When someone comes into
OL,13,Fcontact with our officers and staff,
OL,14,Fthey should be treated with respect
OL,15,Fand professionalism.
OL,17,F"Hutchings' behaviour was vile and
OL,18,Fdegrading and clearly nowhere near the
OL,19,Fexpectation we have of our officers.
OL,26,@tD@NOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
