OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774980702
OL,3,CEx Hampshire police officer carried
OL,4,Cout unwarranted strip searches on
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,F"He was rightly sacked from the force
OL,8,Fwhen his offences first came to light
OL,9,Fin 2007.
OL,11,F"In 2020, when we received another
OL,12,Freport of his offending from around
OL,13,Fthe same time period, we undertook a
OL,14,Fthorough investigation to establish
OL,15,Fthe extent of Hutchings' offending.
OL,17,F"Thanks to the bravery of the victims
OL,18,Fin recalling their experience, and the
OL,19,Fhard work of investigators, Hutchings
OL,20,Fnow faces another spell in prison for
OL,21,Fhis awful behaviour."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
